開啟Impala shell
$ impala-shell

同步Hive數據
$ INVALIDATE METADATA;

列出Table
$ show tables;

列出資料並照時間排序
$ select * from powerdata_minute where `Name` = "LIB-3" order by `Date` asc;

設定Memory
$ set mem_limit=15gb;

對PowerRecord做排序
$ select `time`, `meter_id`, `v` from powerrecord where `meter_id` = "THUC-M0005-server-main" order by `time` limit 100;
